---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout category="business">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-16 text-center">업무절차</h1>

    <!-- Introduction -->
    <div class="w-full mb-12 text-center">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        SCV 파트너스는 체계적이고 전문적인 업무 프로세스를 통해 고객의 주주총회 의결권 확보 및 행사를 지원합니다.<br>
        투명하고 효율적인 절차로 최상의 서비스를 제공합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Process Steps -->
    <div class="w-full">
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Process Flow Line -->
        <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-20 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gray-200"></div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="bg-primary text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-xl font-bold relative z-10">
              1
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-3">의뢰 접수</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• 의뢰 접수</li>
              <li>• 안건 및 상황 분석</li>
              <li>• 제안서 작성</li>
              <li>• 고객사 미팅</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="bg-secondary text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-xl font-bold relative z-10">
              2
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-secondary mb-3">계약 체결</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• 주주명부 수령</li>
              <li>• 견적서 제출</li>
              <li>• 계약 체결</li>
              <li>• 일정 협의</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="bg-accent text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-xl font-bold relative z-10">
              3
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-accent mb-3">의결권 확보</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• 의결권 확보 (주주집 내방, 온라인, 전화응대 등)</li>
              <li>• 위임장 인계</li>
              <li>• 주주성향 보고</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="relative text-center">
            <div class="bg-green-600 text-white w-16 h-16 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-xl font-bold relative z-10">
              4
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-600 mb-3">사후 관리</h3>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>• 주주총회 행사 진행</li>
              <li>• 사후 주주관리 (전화응대 등)</li>
              <li>• 등기 확인 / 업무 종료</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Detailed Process Section -->
    <div class="w-full mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-gray-800">차별화 시스템</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- NDA -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">철저한 보안</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            최고의 전문가로 구성된 위임장 확보 전문 컨설팅 회사<br />
            NDA(기밀유지 협약서) 체결로 인한 고객사와의 절대적인 보안유지
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Risk Management -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">리스크 관리</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            위임장 컴플라이언스 도입(위임장 진위여부 확인 및 법적책임)<br />
            위임장 전문컨설턴트의 자문화된 설득 전략
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 24/7 Support -->
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md border hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-green-600 mb-3">24시간 업무협조</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            사후주주관리제도 운영으로 주주와의 긴밀성 연계유지<br />
            매일 업무 현황보고 및 비상대기팀 운영으로 24시간 업무협조 가능
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Service Features -->
    <div class="w-full mt-16 bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">서비스 특징</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">전문인력 투입</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">5년 이상 경험의 전문 직원들로 구성된 팀</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">매일 현황 보고</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">투명한 진행 상황 공유 및 실시간 업데이트</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-primary rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">안전한 결제 시스템</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">계약금 60-70%, 성공 시 잔금 지급 구조</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">토탈 서비스</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">법무, 공증, 보안까지 원스톱 서비스</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">사후 관리</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">주주총회 이후 지속적인 주주 관리 서비스</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center mt-1">
              <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">높은 성공률</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">일반/특별결의 100%, 경영권분쟁 95% 성공률</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact CTA -->
    <div class="w-full mt-16 bg-primary text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">전문적인 의결권 대행 서비스</h3>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
        체계적인 프로세스와 풍부한 경험으로 최상의 결과를 보장합니다
      </p>
      <div class="text-sm opacity-75">
        문의: <a href="tel:02-556-2260" class="hover:underline">02-556-2260</a> | <a href="mailto:zinaster@naver.com" class="hover:underline">zinaster@naver.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
